headline: New McCormick Directors May Shape Board Priorities And Valuation Upside
summary: McCormick (NYSE:MKC) has added Gavin Hattersley and Rick Dierker to its Board of Directors. Hattersley is the former CEO of Molson Coors and Dierker is the current CEO of Church & Dwight. The appointments represent a refresh of McCormick's leadership structure and governance. McCormick is a global flavor and spice company with a footprint across retail, foodservice, and industrial channels.
